item.title: I Need Help to get it to no-ip [ Deception 317 ] *URGENT HELP NEEDED*
item.dc:creator: @Level_120_Dungeoneer Level 120 Dungeoneering
item.description:
@Level_120_Dungeoneer wrote:

No-IP Duc doesn’t put your server online at all, it just hides your IP address so people won’t find where you live or DoS you. To get your server online, you have to port forward. No-IP is optional. To find a port forwarding guide for your router, go to: http://www.portforward.com/ .
